    <item>
      <title>土耳其市场监管机构为股票限制和高速交易辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/turkey-s-market-watchdog-defends-stock-curbs-high-speed-trading</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其最高市场监管机构否认了有关疫情期间交易限制将被取消的猜测，称这些措施对于市场稳定至关重要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/turkey-s-market-watchdog-defends-stock-curbs-high-speed-trading</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 10:15:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰电力公司 Tauron 计划在 2030 年退出煤炭市场，资本支出达 250 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/polish-power-utility-tauron-plots-coal-exit-in-2030-with-25-billion-capex</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着欧盟最依赖煤炭的国家加快能源转型，波兰第二大电力公司 Tauron Polska Energia SA 计划在本世纪末淘汰所有燃煤机组。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/polish-power-utility-tauron-plots-coal-exit-in-2030-with-25-billion-capex</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 09:51:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经济不确定性导致德国商业前景低迷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/german-business-outlook-slumps-amid-economic-uncertainty</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国 12 月份商业预期下滑，凸显出欧洲最大经济体面临的挑战，因为提前选举可能会导致政府更迭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/german-business-outlook-slumps-amid-economic-uncertainty</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 09:08:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长雷恩认为随着物价企稳，利率方向明确</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/ecb-s-rehn-sees-direction-clear-on-rates-as-inflation-stabilizes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员奥利·雷恩表示，随着通胀率开始稳定在 2% 左右的目标水平，欧洲央行利率将继续下行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/ecb-s-rehn-sees-direction-clear-on-rates-as-inflation-stabilizes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国工资上涨后交易员预计英国央行降息幅度将减少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/traders-see-fewer-boe-interest-rate-cuts-after-jump-in-uk-wages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数据显示工资涨幅超过预期，这是通胀压力困扰英国经济的最新证据，交易员削减了对英国进一步降息的押注，债券价格下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/traders-see-fewer-boe-interest-rate-cuts-after-jump-in-uk-wages</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 07:56:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>T. Rowe 因财政风险上调美国国债收益率预期至 6%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/treasury-yields-at-6-are-possible-on-fiscal-risks-t-rowe-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[普信公司表示，随着美国财政困境恶化，且唐纳德·特朗普的政策有助于维持通胀高企，10 年期美国国债收益率可能在 20 多年来首次攀升至 6%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/treasury-yields-at-6-are-possible-on-fiscal-risks-t-rowe-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 07:00:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰晤士水务公司债权人质疑30亿英镑救助贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/thames-water-set-for-pivotal-hearing-on-3-billion-rescue-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[代表泰晤士水务公司竞争对手的律师周二向伦敦一位法官表示，泰晤士水务公司计划获得的 30 亿英镑（38 亿美元）救助贷款将“勒索”该公司，并将控制权移交给优先债权人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/thames-water-set-for-pivotal-hearing-on-3-billion-rescue-loan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价下跌，因中国经济数据不佳影响前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-17</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国经济数据未能消除人们对最大原油进口国消费放缓的担忧，油价连续第二天走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-17</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 23:30:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
